{"tid":935180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國「女德班」: 換男友會爛手爛腳","createTime":"2018-12-09T23:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T06:29:12.000Z","uid":75969,"like":36,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"679f6f38b6a78f5de001d29785c1db0c6478bfe6","tid":935180,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T23:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181209/_2018120918505254263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181209%2F_2018120918505254263.jpg&h=45803196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遼寧撫順的「女德班」去年被責令關閉後，今年再在溫州捲土重來，並開辦「親子夏令營」，不但向未成年少女灌輸婚姻四原則，即「打不還手，罵不還口，逆來順受，堅決不離婚」，而且更新增「換男友會爛手爛腳」等觀念。<br />\n<br />\n該「親子夏令營」由溫州傳統文化促進會舉辦，而當中的教師大多來自曾舉辦「女德班」的撫順市傳統文化教育學校，並針對5-18歲未成年少女，教授「孝道」、「女德」等課題。從媒體偷拍的影片可見，該夏令營宣揚不少男尊女卑的觀念，包括婚姻四原則，即「打不還手、罵不還口、逆來順受、堅決不離婚」等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦向現場學員播放影片，影片中的少女指，「我將自己打扮得那麼妖豔，穿得那麼時尚又那麼暴露，不就等同於教別人來汙辱我、來強姦我是一樣的嗎？」，同時更播放有關女孩子頻換男朋友會爛手爛腳，最後需要截肢的恐怖畫面。據悉，該夏令營共有56名青少年參加，當中44人為女生。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民其後紛紛留言，指責該夏令營是邪教，又指「什麼年代了，居然會有這樣言論」，以及「什麼樣的父母才會送孩子去這樣的地方，簡直是邪教啊」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/883801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F883801&d=G0HW2Q3MzJnhCWbogdeJGdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5e8b43c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F883801&h=7d85aa89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/883801</a>"},{"pid":"a84b2497826f1e0ab29427c9af7c40994f894094","tid":935180,"uid":48234,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T23:37:00.000Z","msg":"呢啲夏令營嚟香港搞埋啦,講埋食洋湯都會損手爛腳"},{"pid":"eb84980ddda251522fcafe0de4cba624ae7fb052","tid":935180,"uid":169676,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T23:42:22.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n<br />\n學成龍話齋女人是需要管的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682e68db8b0674077ea2940409f07c59a1f6578b","tid":935180,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a970066237b75568c2ab6053fa3fdaffa4d233","tid":935180,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T23:48:46.000Z","msg":"引入香港唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee04d6d3bec8e1e041e3a21d2afe34fc0d577f72","tid":935180,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T23:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e130b3f97faf6caa56de8e5954ac9db536d350e","tid":935180,"uid":8171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a84b2497826f1e0ab29427c9af7c40994f894094","tid":935180,"uid":48234,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T23:37:00.000Z","msg":"呢啲夏令營嚟香港搞埋啦,講埋食洋湯都會損手爛腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T00:43:37.000Z","msg":"食洋腸會爛西"},{"pid":"3b58cc4a8d1f4e63627d706001eea80781a216e9","tid":935180,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"一眾連登仔表示支持"},{"pid":"a6b0cf88842893484af4a0fa0eee70f2fc058efa","tid":935180,"uid":1139,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:17:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e4238d36f7e2bf47d07085b7f4879b456e37f85","tid":935180,"uid":91633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:19:38.000Z","msg":"平安谷先係正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7339c4877781a88f5e6e22498e880ee23d6ac151","tid":935180,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"去台灣開班啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dacb0bf977a00e40d05cba6469e415225165605","tid":935180,"uid":75139,"like":0,